import React from 'react';
import scrumate from './../image/scrumate.png';
import { Apple, Shop } from '@material-ui/icons';
import { Box, Card, CardMedia, CardContent, CardActions, IconButton } from '@material-ui/core';

export default class Apps extends React.Component {

  render() {
    return (
        <Box color="#263238" width={2/5} align="center" display="flex" flexDirection="row" justifyContent="space-between">
          <Box color="#263238" width={1/2} align="center">
            <Card>
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                image={scrumate}
              />
            </Card>
            <CardActions>
              <IconButton aria-label="appStore">
                <Apple/>
              </IconButton>
              <IconButton aria-label="googlePlay">
                <Shop/>
              </IconButton>
            </CardActions>
          </Box>
            <Box color="#263238" width={1/2} align="center">
              <Card>
                <CardMedia
                  component="img"
                  image={scrumate}
                />
              </Card>
              <CardActions>
                <IconButton aria-label="appStore">
                  <Apple/>
                </IconButton>
                <IconButton aria-label="googlePlay">
                  <Shop/>
                </IconButton>
              </CardActions>
            </Box>
        </Box>
    );
  }
}
